{{作品名稱|name=''The Phone Call''|tw=自殺熱線|zh=自杀热线}}是一部2013年的[[英國|英國]]劇情[[短片|短片]]，{{link-en|麥特·科比|Mat Kirkby}}執導，編劇由麥特和{{link-en|詹姆斯·盧卡斯|James Lucas (screenwriter)}}共同擔當，並拿下[[第87屆奧斯卡金像獎|第87屆奧斯卡金像獎]][[奧斯卡最佳實景短片獎|最佳實景短片獎]]。<ref name="87th">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-30835975 |title=Oscars 2015: Nominations list |accessdate=24 January 2015 |date=23 February 2015 |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]}}</ref>
影片講述擔任[[危機熱線|危機熱線]]顧問的 Heather ([[莎莉·霍金斯|莎莉·霍金斯]] 飾)接到一通因妻子離世而想不開的諮詢電話，她一邊安撫對方，一邊與時間賽跑找出這位匿名通話者。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/feb/19/from-burger-ads-to-oscar-nomination-the-phone-call|title=How two British short film-makers turned rejection into an Oscars nod|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=19 February 2015|accessdate=15 January 2016|first=Andrew|last=Pulver}}</ref>

